{
  "id": "adv_main_03_01_01",
  "title": "BIG4編1章1話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ約束の時間だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's almost time for our appointment",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "私……納得いきません\nいくら三枝さんの言うことでも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… I can't accept this\nEven if it's Mr. Saegusa's words…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 10.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さんの気持ちは分かるよ\n俺だって本心から納得してる訳じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how you feel‚ Hashimoto-san\nI'm not fully convinced either",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんにせよ……まずは本人達と話してみないとな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway… we need to talk to them first",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I understand",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 24.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "あ……い、いらっしゃいましたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… th-they're here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 24.2333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2733.333333400001,
          "startTime": 26.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 26.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのみなさん\n丁重なお出迎え、感謝します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone from Hoshimi Productions\nThank you for your warm welcome",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 35.2184580485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ようこそ、スリクスのみなさん\n三枝の呼び出しに応じていただきありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Welcome‚ everyone from IIIX\nThank you for responding to Saegusa's invitation",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9517913818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 41.6517913818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYで見事優勝した星見プロさんが\nkana達に一体なんの用ですかぁ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What business does Hoshimi Pro‚ who brilliantly won I-UNITY\nhave with kana and the others?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6517913818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それは……三枝からご説明いたしますので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That… will be explained by Saegusa",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1184580485,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10533.3333333,
          "startTime": 59.6517913818
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12466.666666599998,
          "startTime": 61.5851247151
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 54.0851247151
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 54.3184580485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "代表の三枝を呼んで来ますので、少々お待ち下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll go get our representative‚ Mr. Saegusa. Please wait a moment",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1184580485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYの直後にお会いして以来ですね\nあれから、大変だったようですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while since we met right after I-UNITY\nIt seems you've had a tough time since then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2851247151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね\nプレタポルテを退所して、フリーになって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that's right\nWe left Pret-a-Porter‚ became freelancers…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4851247151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "そして、BIG4の座を失った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And lost our place in the BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.7851247151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 77.6517913818
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 77.8851247151
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（バンプロでの資金横領やI-UNITYでの）\n（不正が追及され姫野さんは逮捕）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The embezzlement at Ban Production and)\n(the fraud at I-UNITY were investigated‚ and Himeno-san was arrested)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4184580485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（プレタポルテもアイドル業界から手を引き）\n（スリクスは居場所を失ってしまった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Pret-a-Porter also withdrew from the idol industry)\n(IIIX lost their place)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9517913818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（その後、スリクスは事務所と決別）\n（独立して再出発したらしい ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(After that‚ IIIX parted ways with the agency)\n(It seems they started over independently)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3517913818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 98.2184580485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "ま、姫野とか事務所とかどうでもいいんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I don't care about Himeno or the agency",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3517913818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "だって、最強は――kana達スリクスだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because the strongest is still us‚ IIIX",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2184580485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "私達、セルフプロデュースも出来ますから\nすぐにBIG4に返り咲きます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can self-produce too\nWe'll be back in the BIG4 soon",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2951247151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……あのね。今回の一件で私達、とんでもない\nイメージダウンで仕事を何本も打ち切られてるのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Listen. This incident has caused us\na huge image drop and we've lost several jobs",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2184580485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、フリーになるということは\n自分達で仕事を取ってこないといけないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ being freelance means\nwe have to find work on our own",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.6851247151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "スケジュール管理やギャラを交渉したり\n外部とのやり取りだってあるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manage schedules‚ negotiate fees\nDeal with external parties…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4851247151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのはmihoが得意なんだし\n全部お任せでいいっしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're good at that stuff‚ miho\nWe can leave it all to you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3184580485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 137.7184580485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと。私も得意なんだけど？\nファッションブランドを立ち上げたこともあるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey. I'm good at it too‚ you know?\nI've even launched a fashion brand before",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.9184580485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "あー、ダメダメ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ no way‚ no way",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8184580485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "……なんですって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What did you say?",
        "id": ""
      },
